        <title>Python&#43;tkinter的GUI程序创建以及使用-20230723</title>
        <link>https://news-epoch.github.io/p/python-tkinter%E7%9A%84gui%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-20230723/</link>
